$\Psi = \frac{\lambda}{2} \text{tr}\left(\matrice{E}\right)^2 + \mu \matrice{E}:\matrice{E}$

* Unstable under compression 
* $\nu = 0.49$ for quasi-incompressibility
  * Soft tissues are often modelled as incompressible materials

