$$            \vect{u}\left(\textcolor{Blue}{\vect{x}}, \textcolor{LGreen}{\para}\right) = \sum\limits_{i=1}^m \textcolor{Blue}{\overline{\vect{u}}_i(\vect{x})} ~\textcolor{LGreen}{\prod_{j=1}^{\beta}\lambda_i^j(\mu^j)} $$
:::
:::

